Pre-Game Insights: The Proteas' fixtures for the Super 8 stage of the 2024 T20 World Cup have been confirmed.
The undefeated Proteas earned a place in Group 2, along with defending champions England, as well as co-hosts West Indies and the USA.
The Proteas face reigning T20 World champions England in St Lucia on 21 June in what is sure to be a thrilling fixture.
